WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A12
</SO>
<CO>
   U.BA AMR
</CO>
<IN>
AEROSPACE (ARO)
AIRLINES (AIR)
</IN>
<LP>
   WASHINGTON -- British Aerospace PLC's U.S. unit said that
AMR Corp.'s AMR Eagle Inc. regional airline subsidiary has
placed a follow-on order for 35 BAE Jetstream Super 31s, with
